Personal Banking



Home
Personal Banking
Online and Mobile Banking



Online and Mobile Banking
Pay | Bank | Deposit


MBT offers a comprehensive suite of mobile and online banking services providing you with the tools to take control of your money and to simplify how you manage your finances.




Control
View statements, monitor activity, transfer funds, view check images, pay bills and make loan payments in just a few clicks.
 


Convenience 
You decide when it’s time to bank; manage your accounts on your time anytime, anywhere.


Safe and Secure
Your personal information is protected by advanced encryption technology to prevent unauthorized access. Visit the MBT Security Center for more information on how we protect you.


free technology
Manage all of your MBT accounts wherever and whenever with these free services. Access rates may apply depending on your carrier.




 




make deposits
24/7 access to deposit checks or cash




Mobile Deposit
Just point click and snap - to deposit checks from almost anywhere, anytime with any device.
View the Demo >>


MBT ATMs
Deposit up to 30 checks and cash at MBT ATMs and you can get image confirmation on your receipt.
Find an MBT ATM >>


Direct Deposit
The fastest, most convenient way to automatically deposit your funds direct from your employer and other sources of income.
Download Form (PDF)




 




MAKE PAYMENTS
Pay bills or people, quickly and conveniently 




Online Bill Pay*
Save time, make your payments the smart, easy and secure way with online banking or with MBT's Mobile App, without the hassle of writing a check.
View the Demo >>
To Enroll: Click the bill payment button in Online Banking!
*Online Bill Pay is a free service, however, a $7.00 monthly inactivity fee applies if the service is unused for 30 days. The fee stops on the next billing cycle if online bill pay is resumed.


MOBILE PURCHASING
Load your MBT debit card on your phone or device. You can you can use your eligible device at merchant locations nationwide to conveniently make purchases.
Learn More >>


MBT PopMoney
A convenient way to receive and send money to another person without cash or checks—all you need is their email address or mobile number. Access this service in Online Bill Pay.




 
Enroll in Online Banking >>
 
Download the MBT Mobile App
 












