Business Banking



Home
Business Banking
Payroll & HR Solutions



Payroll, Human Resource & Employee Benefits Solutions
Reduce Costs. Improve Cashflow.


Monroe Bank & Trust, in partnership with Sage Payroll Services® makes it easy for businesses to streamline the entire payroll process. From payroll calculations and direct deposit to detailed reporting and tax management, Sage has a simple and cost-effective payroll solution.
 
Choose the Sage Program that is right for your business
Sage Payroll Services grows with your business, so you can upgrade whenever necessary.




Self Service 
The Self Service Payroll solution is designed for businesses with 10 or fewer employees.
For a low, monthly fee of just $49.95** you’ll enjoy unlimited payroll processing. Plus, full management of payroll taxes is included, so you don’t have to worry about costly fines and penalties. Simply key in your payroll data, and Sage will take it from there.
This valuable service also includes:

Convenient online access so you can process payroll wherever your business takes you.
Free direct deposit for you and your employees.
Federal, state and local tax administration to guarantee accurate and timely tax filing — it even includes a penalty-free tax filing guarantee.
A variety of online payroll management reports.
Vacation and sick time tracking.
Online paycheck information and W-2 access for your employees.
Access to Certified Payroll Experts by phone, email or online chat.
Six-month money back guarantee.



Full Service                           
Full Service Payroll solutions are available for larger businesses or for those with more complex payroll management needs. Full Service Payroll solutions are available at competitive prices through our partnership with Sage. This more robust service includes all of the features of the Self Service Payroll solution — and so much more.
 

An innovative time and attendance solution that can help improve accuracy and eliminate the hassles of data entry.
Pay-as-you-go workers’ compensation plan — no up-front premiums or year-end audits.
Tools, resources, templates and more available through the HR Compliance Center to help you save time and money.
A secure, online data management system for storing all critical employee information.
Easy enrollment and administration of employee benefits online.





    
Request a Business Evaluation
 
Services are offered through Sage Payroll Services® and its licensed affiliates. Sage Payroll Services® is a separate entity and not affiliated with Monroe Bank & Trust.












