About
Monroe Bank & Trust is located at the address 1000 S Monroe St in Monroe, Michigan 48161.  They can be contacted via phone at (734) 242-1701 for pricing, hours and directions.  Monroe Bank & Trust specializes in Vacation Property, Mobile Homes, Apartments.  Monroe Bank & Trust has an annual sales volume of 2.  .For more information contact Pat  Orr, Branch Manager or  go to www.mbandt.comMonroe Bank & Trust provides Banking Services, Collections, Financial Services to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Monroe Bank & Trust view the map to the right.  For reviews of Monroe Bank & Trust see below.









